						<summary>

						<p>This is an undated inscription of the reign of the Noḷamba-Pallava king <hi rend="bold">Noḷa[mbādhirāja].</hi> It states that the stone was set up in memory of a certain person who died by entering into the fire on account of the death of some one (name lost).</p>						

